cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.MM 

The paper focuses on self-supervised learning of visual features using textual context, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of deep learning techniques for this purpose also falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) as it deals with multi-modal retrieval. Finally, the paper's experiments involve image classification and object detection, which are common topics in multimedia (cs.MM).
